1. Danas sam **pogođen** lošim vestima. (Today I am *affected* by bad news.)
2. Nakon što je izgubio posao, bio je **pogođen** depresijom. (After losing his job, he was *affected* by depression.)
3. Fudbaler je **pogođen** loptom u glavu. (The football player was *hit* in the head by the ball.)
4. Publika je bila **pogođena** izvođenjem opere. (The audience was *moved* by the performance of the opera.)
5. Zgrada je bila **pogođena** zemljotresom. (The building was *hit* by an earthquake.)
6. Njegova tačnost uvek me **pogađa**. (His accuracy always *hits* me.)
7. Uspela sam da **pogodim** metu iz prve. (I managed to *hit* the target on the first try.)
8. Iako nije pogodio pravu reč, bio je blizu. (Although he didn't *guess* the right word, he was close.)
9. Njegovo izvinjenje me je **pogodilo**. (His apology *touched* me.)
10. Moramo **pogoditi** tačno vreme sastanka. (We need to *agree on* the exact time of the meeting.)